---

<Layout
  title="Ángel Sánchez — Desarrollador Full Stack"
  description="Portfolio de Ángel Sánchez. Desarrollador Full Stack en C#/.NET, Angular y Java. Diseño y código limpios, productos que escalan."
>
  <!-- =========================================================
       HERO
  ========================================================== -->
  <section
    id="inicio"
    class="relative pt-36 md:pt-44 pb-24 md:pb-32 overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="hero-ambient" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container relative">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left column (text) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="section-label mb-8" data-reveal="fade">
            <span>Portfolio · v2025</span>
          </div>

          <h1 data-reveal="mask" class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-[5.5rem] font-bold font-display tracking-[-0.025em] leading-[0.95] text-[#0A1931]">
            Construyo<br />
            <span class="text-gradient">software</span> que<br />
            funciona.
          </h1>

          <p data-hero="sub" data-reveal="lines" data-reveal-delay="0.3" class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#4A6A87] mt-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            Soy <strong class="text-[#0A1931] font-semibold">Ángel Sánchez</strong>, desarrollador Full Stack.
            Especializado en <span class="text-[#1A3D63] font-medium">C#/.NET</span>,
            <span class="text-[#1A3D63] font-medium">Angular</span> y
            <span class="text-[#1A3D63] font-medium">Java/Spring</span>. Diseño limpio, código mantenible, productos que escalan.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-10" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="0.5">
            <a href="#proyectos" class="btn btn-primary" data-cursor="hover">
              Ver proyectos
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:srangeldev@gmail.com" class="btn btn-secondary" data-cursor="hover">
              Hablemos
            </a>
            <a href="/cv.pdf" download class="btn btn-ghost" data-cursor="hover">
              Descargar CV
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Status row -->
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap" data-reveal="fade" data-reveal-delay="0.7">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
              <span class="relative flex w-2.5 h-2.5">
                <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#2F7D4F] opacity-60 animate-ping"></span>
                <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-[#2F7D4F]"></span>
              </span>
              <span class="text-sm text-[#4A6A87]">Disponible para nuevos proyectos</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-4 w-px bg-[rgba(26,61,99,0.18)]"></div>
            <span class="text-sm text-[#4A6A87]">
              <span class="text-[#0A1931] font-semibold">3+</span> años de experiencia
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right column (info card) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5" data-hero="aside">
          <div class="card p-7 md:p-8" data-reveal="scale" data-reveal-delay="0.4" data-tilt data-tilt-max="6" data-cursor="hover">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-7">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#1A3D63] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold font-display text-lg">A</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0A1931]">Ángel Sánchez</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-[#7895AE]">@srangeldev</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#4A7FA7] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase">/ Perfil</span>
            </div>

            <dl class="space-y-4 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-[rgba(26,61,99,0.08)]">
                <dt class="text-[#7895AE]">Rol</dt>
                <dd class="text-[#0A1931] font-medium">Full Stack Developer</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-[rgba(26,61,99,0.08)]">
                <dt class="text-[#7895AE]">Ubicación</dt>
                <dd class="text-[#0A1931] font-medium">España · Remoto</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-[rgba(26,61,99,0.08)]">
                <dt class="text-[#7895AE]">Foco</dt>
                <dd class="text-[#0A1931] font-medium">Backend & DX</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <dt class="text-[#7895AE]">Estado</dt>
                <dd class="text-[#2F7D4F] font-medium flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#2F7D4F]"></span> Disponible
                </dd>
              </div>
            </dl>

            <div class="mt-7 pt-6 border-t border-[rgba(26,61,99,0.08)]">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-center">
                <div>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-[#0A1931]">10+</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-[#7895AE] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mt-1">Proyectos</div>
                </div>
                <div class="border-x border-[rgba(26,61,99,0.08)]">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-[#0A1931]">3+</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-[#7895AE] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mt-1">Años</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-[#0A1931]">∞</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-[#7895AE] uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mt-1">Ganas</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- =========================================================
       PROJECTS
  ========================================================== -->
  <section id="proyectos" class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6 mb-16">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label mb-5" data-reveal="fade"><span>Trabajo seleccionado</span></div>
          <h2 data-reveal="mask" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold font-display tracking-[-0.025em] leading-[1] text-[#0A1931]">
            Proyectos<br />destacados.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p data-reveal="lines" data-reveal-delay="0.15" class="text-[#4A6A87] text-base md:text-lg max-w-md">
          Una pequeña muestra de lo que he construido recientemente. Cada uno
          resuelve un problema real con tecnologías pensadas para durar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        {projects.map((p, i) => (
          <div data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay={`${i * 0.12}`}>
            <ProjectCard {...p} />
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- =========================================================
       ABOUT PREVIEW
  ========================================================== -->
  <section data-section="about" class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#EEF4FA]/60 border-y border-[rgba(26,61,99,0.06)]">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5" data-parallax="-0.15">
          <div class="section-label mb-5" data-reveal="fade"><span>Sobre mí</span></div>
          <h2 data-reveal="words" data-reveal-stagger="0.07" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display tracking-[-0.025em] leading-[1.05] text-[#0A1931]">
            Detrás del código, una forma de pensar.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6" data-parallax="0.08">
          <p data-reveal="lines" class="text-lg text-[#4A6A87] leading-relaxed">
            Llevo más de tres años construyendo software full stack. Me interesan
            los sistemas que envejecen bien: aquellos que el equipo siguiente
            puede leer, extender y desplegar sin miedo.
          </p>

          <blockquote data-reveal="mask" class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-[#1A3D63] py-2">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-display text-[#0A1931] leading-snug">
              «El mejor código es el que <em class="text-[#1A3D63] not-italic">no necesitas explicar</em>.»
            </p>
          </blockquote>

          <p data-reveal="lines" data-reveal-delay="0.1" class="text-[#4A6A87] leading-relaxed">
            Trabajo con C#/.NET y Java en backend, Angular y TypeScript en
            frontend, y me encargo de la infraestructura con Docker, Nginx y
            GitHub Actions. Cuido los detalles porque la diferencia entre
            "funciona" y "es excelente" suele estar en ellos.
          </p>

          <div class="pt-2" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="0.2">
            <a href="/sobre-mi" class="btn btn-secondary" data-cursor="hover">
              Conoce más sobre mí
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- =========================================================
       STACK
  ========================================================== -->
  <section id="stack" class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
        <div class="section-label mb-5 justify-center" data-reveal="fade"><span>Stack técnico</span></div>
        <h2 data-reveal="mask" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold font-display tracking-[-0.025em] leading-[1] text-[#0A1931]">
          Las herramientas que uso<br />
          <span class="text-gradient">a diario.</span>
        </h2>
        <p data-reveal="lines" data-reveal-delay="0.15" class="text-[#4A6A87] text-base md:text-lg mt-6">
          Tres bloques: lo que sirve los datos, lo que los muestra y lo que
          mantiene todo en marcha.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-14">
        {
          stackGroups.map((group, gi) => (
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-7" data-reveal="up">
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[#4A7FA7] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase">
                  / 0{gi + 1}
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold font-display text-[#0A1931]">
                  {group.title}
                </h3>
                <div class="flex-grow h-px bg-[rgba(26,61,99,0.08)]" />
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                {group.items.map((tech, ti) => (
                  <div data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay={`${ti * 0.06}`} data-tilt data-tilt-max="10" data-cursor="hover">
                    <TechStack name={tech.name} icon={tech.icon} level={tech.level} />
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <!-- Marquee de tecnologías -->
      <div class="mt-20 -mx-4">
        <div class="marquee" data-marquee data-marquee-speed="40" data-marquee-direction="left">
          <div class="marquee__track">
            <span class="marquee__item">C# / .NET</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Java / Spring</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Angular</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Astro</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Tailwind</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Node.js</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Docker</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">GitHub Actions</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">SQL Server</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Redis</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="marquee mt-3" data-marquee data-marquee-speed="50" data-marquee-direction="right">
          <div class="marquee__track">
            <span class="marquee__item">Nginx</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Linux</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Git</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Cloudflare</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">REST / GraphQL</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">SOLID</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">DDD</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">CI / CD</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Testing</span>
            <span class="marquee__item">Clean Architecture</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- =========================================================
       MI ENTORNO (Terminal)
  ========================================================== -->
  <section data-section="env" class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#EEF4FA]/60 border-y border-[rgba(26,61,99,0.06)]">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5" data-parallax="-0.12">
          <div class="section-label mb-5" data-reveal="fade"><span>Mi entorno</span></div>
          <h2 data-reveal="words" data-reveal-stagger="0.08" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display tracking-[-0.025em] leading-[1.05] text-[#0A1931]">
            Una terminal, un buen workflow.
          </h2>
          <p data-reveal="lines" data-reveal-delay="0.15" class="text-[#4A6A87] mt-6 leading-relaxed">
            Vivo entre el editor y la consola. Buenas convenciones, scripts
            sencillos y despliegues automatizados — eso me devuelve tiempo
            para lo que importa: pensar y construir.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7" data-reveal="mask" data-parallax="0.06">
          <TerminalConsole />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- =========================================================
       CTA
  ========================================================== -->
  <section data-section="cta" class="relative py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card p-10 md:p-16 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-reveal="scale" data-tilt data-tilt-max="4" data-cursor="hover">
        <div class="section-label mb-5 justify-center" data-reveal="fade" data-reveal-delay="0.2"><span>Trabajemos juntos</span></div>
        <h2 data-reveal="words" data-reveal-delay="0.3" data-reveal-stagger="0.07" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold font-display tracking-[-0.025em] leading-[1] text-[#0A1931]">
          ¿Tienes una idea? Hablemos.
        </h2>
        <p data-reveal="lines" data-reveal-delay="0.5" class="text-[#4A6A87] text-base md:text-lg mt-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Cuéntame qué quieres construir. Respondo rápido y sin compromiso.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-10 justify-center" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="0.7">
          <a href="mailto:srangeldev@gmail.com" class="btn btn-primary" data-cursor="hover">
            Enviar email
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/srangeldev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary" data-cursor="hover">
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
